title: Tarrabyte - Something Clever Goes Here
description:
Hey, 
So you are prolly wondering what this is all about? Right? 

Well, if you are a fateful pirate like me and keep up with Pirate news, you will know that the bay is on of the leading sites in torrenting/sharing.

Not just "illegal" torrents but torrents that help change the world. 

Blah blah blah you don't care.

"what is this torrent?"

this is a torrent of some of my...Well.. Work...Some of my music, I'm seeding out my work on the bay to any one that loves electronic music. I want to test an idea out and see how well it works. 

"Don't you want to get paid for your work?"

I do, and I'm trying. I love making music and I love working on what ever I can in FL. Music is basically my life. I'm not going to lie and say I'm amazing. I want feedback. I want people to tell me what I can do to fix my mistakes. How I can tweak something and make it sound cooler. 

I am proud to be at the point I am at right now. I can definitely say I feel like I've come a long way, but I'm not where I want to be, and I know I'm no where near the Armin Van Burren or Deadmau5 or Sander Van Doorn stage. Maybe one day. 

Till then, I will try my best.

=========


ANY HOW:

Please share my music and have others come and see me at my blog etc and tell me how I'm doing even leave comments! 
PS read the note I left in the torrent.

Please help an electronic artist make it some place! 

-HERO!
